cleanReq:{[req] :(key req)#(`qid`wid`uid`expr`type!("G"$;"G"$;"G"$;::;`$))@'req; }
sendState:{[]                                                                             DP "sending state to ",(string count .quagga.w)," clients";
  {neg[x] -8! (`state;y "value `.")} ./: flip value exec sockets,h from .quagga.w
  }

